.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-REMOTE-BALANCE-VARIANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-remote-balance-variance \- FEAT-2958 peer-remote-balance-variance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-remote-balance-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the variance of remote balances per peer across all channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2958).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBremote_balance_variance_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
